      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the mince is beginning to brown, add the <strong>remaining soy sauce</strong>, <strong>Chinese rice wine </strong>and <strong>hoisin sauce </strong>to the pan and stir it all together</p><p>Add your<strong> honey </strong>to the pan and cook for a further 4 min or until the mince is cooked through (no pink meat!) and a little sticky – this is your <strong>honey hoisin lean pork</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
