    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> drained noodles</strong> to the pan with the pork and give everything a good mix up – these are your <strong>honey hoisin lean pork noodles</strong></p><p>Tip: Add a splash of starchy cooking water if your sauce is looking a little dry!</p>",
