    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the<strong> honey hoisin lean pork noodles</strong> with the <strong>smashed sesame cucumber</strong> to the side</p><p>Garnish with the <strong>remaining chilli flakes </strong>(not a fan of spice? Just add a little!)</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
